    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we want to be completely transparent: this is a genuinely outstanding example that is rare to find on the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and all body panels are straight and true. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim pieces, and all controls, buttons, and displays functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, with no leaks, no unusual noises, and strong, responsive performance. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in excellent working order, and the vehicle has been well-maintained throughout its life. This is the kind of used car you can purchase with full confidence, knowing you're getting something truly special.",
